{"title":"在篝火边","authors":["姚成友"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":12,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"在篝火边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士　姚成友"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日落西山进林海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"堆堆篝火烧起来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士火边纵谈笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滚滚豪情涌胸怀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，井冈山上传火种，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烧遍千山和万寨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红红的火光映刀影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命先辈把路开："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火边煮小米，火边煨野菜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火边擦刀枪，火边守哨台，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"篝火就是革命火呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化出万杆红旗来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化出万杆红旗来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗下站起新一代！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接过火把接过枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"豪情壮志永不改："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火边补军衣，火边打草鞋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火边读毛选，火边想世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身在深山篝火旁呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红心飞向云天外！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"非洲的闪电南越的雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉美的风暴扑面来……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士愿作火一团呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化作红霞漫天开！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}